high_descs: turn right and walk towards the door then turn left and walk straight towards the stove and turn left and walk straight then turn left at the counter
pick up the knife next to the lettuce
slice the lettuce with the knife
turn left and walk towards the dishwasher then turn right and walk straight to the fridge
open the fridge and put the knife inside and close it
turn right and then turn right again and walk straight to the stove then turn left and then straight and then left again at the counter
pick up one slice of lettuce from the counter
turn left and walk straight then turn right towards the fridge
open the fridge and put the lettuce slice on the middle shelf and close the fridge, then open it and take the lettuce out
turn right then turn right again and walk towards the stove then left and straight and then turn right towards the window
put the lettuce slice into the garbage can near the window
anns.task_desc: Cut a slice of lettuce then throw away the lettuce in the garbage can

high_descs: Walk around the counter and face it.
Pick up the knife.
Slice the lettuce on the counter.
Walk around the counter to the fridge.
Put the knife in the freezer.
Turn around, walk around the counter, and face the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Walk around the counter to the fridge.
Put the slice of lettuce in the fridge, wait, and take the slice of lettuce out of the fridge.
Turn around, and walk around the counter to the window.
Drop the slice of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Drop a cold slice of lettuce in front of the window.

high_descs: Turn right and go around to the other side of the island.
Pick up the knife from the island.
Slice the head of lettuce laying on the island.
Turn left and move across the room to the fridge.
Put the knife on the top shelf in the fridge to the left of the frying pan.
Turn around and move back around to the other side of the island.
Pick up a piece of lettuce from the island.
Turn left and move across the room to the fridge.
Chill the lettuce on the second shelf of the fridge for a few seconds and take it back out.
Turn around and move to the trash can across the room to the trash can on the left of the stove.
Throw the lettuce into the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw away the cooled piece of lettuce.
